They still need to clean up a lot of stuff.
Some champs don't have their full lores like {{champion:72}} {{champion:75}} {{champion:82}}
Some champs don't even have a place in runeterra for now,like {{champion:10}} {{champion:54}} {{champion:31}} 
Some lore pieces are still hard to find,like {{champion:101}} ,{{champion:429}} {{champion:268}} 

